reviewText:
The stories were enjoyable, but one of the stories had Oscar the
Grouch actually quote one of the Gospels and make what Our Lord
said a joke.  I threw it in the garbage, and was amazed that
Sesame St. did this,  I think highly of their work.
I have a daughter with a mental disability and she loves watching sesame street. This is a wonderful addition to her collection.  It was received very promptly also.
